&gt; expert, or the ones desperately grieving, or  lately, religious nuts! 
&gt;  
&gt;  I&#39;ve said it over and over and over and over and over and  
&gt; over--expectation will create the voices you want to hear. If you are  seeking Jesus, that 
&gt; is exactly what you are going to get and you&#39;ll swear  it&#39;s God gospel 
&gt; freaking truth, and the rest of us should bow down to you. I  think y&#39;all know 
&gt; who I&#39;m talking about. 
&gt;  
&gt;  I am uncertain if one can ask for certain spirits, or if even  that tends 
&gt; to create what one wans. I think maybe it works the same as the  above. I 
&gt; don&#39;t ask for any specific spirits/entities, I don&#39;t ask questions,  I just 
&gt; let them talk and try not to influance it. If I have question, I  might think 
&gt; it, and most of the time they&#39;ll answer, wiht out me  asking.  That could be 
&gt; just creating want I want to hear as well--don&#39;t  know.
&gt;  
&gt;  I don&#39;t have to be on these groups and I don&#39;t have make   boxes, except 
&gt; for my own use. I think the messages are personal in  nature, no one is going 
&gt; to hear it the same, and it&#39;s about worthless as  &quot;evidence&quot;. We get enough 
&gt; that&#39;s shareable to show others that it&#39;s real,  and I think that is about 
&gt; the best that can be hoped for. I think, and it is  only my opinion, that 
&gt; &quot;evidence&quot; at so called haunted areas is just what is  expected, I really 
&gt; don&#39;t think it proves anything.
&gt;  
&gt;  Then, there the bullies that want all this to conform to their  wishes, 
&gt; and we saw more examples of that with the recent e-bay auction,  and y&#39;all 
&gt; know who you are! If no one sells boxes, no one builds boxes, its&#39;  that 
&gt; simple! Parts and radios are not free, and why the hell should we be  expected to 
&gt; spend endless hours on this stuff for nothing!?
&gt;  
&gt;  I know, I know --sacrilege!I know, I know --sacrilege!&lt;WBR&gt;-- I should be 
&gt; banned from all  groups and box work, burned at the stake, tarred and 
&gt; feathered, run out I say anything!?
